    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1029890/extras/99fedf9ebefb6af3e6a2c22535ee3920.poster.avif?t=1771007594\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1029890/extras/99fedf9ebefb6af3e6a2c22535ee3920.webm?t=1771007594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1029890/extras/99fedf9ebefb6af3e6a2c22535ee3920.mp4?t=1771007594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这部备受赞誉的续作重新定义了该屡获殊荣的系列作品。化身一名演员，应怀揣诡异意图的导演之邀，登上神秘古怪的远洋客轮进行演出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过往表演的回响扭曲成畸形记忆，道具化作威胁逼近，舞台与自我的边界开始崩塌。每行进一步，都需完成导演谜一般的要求，你将不断自问：为了完美演绎角色，你究竟能付出何等代价？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由现代恐怖游戏大师Bloober Team打造的《Layers of Fear 2》，在瞬息万变的噩梦般环境中呈现了一场电影化的叙事盛宴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1029890/extras/3c64e4ffcd07f9fe296f1a80f52998c1.poster.avif?t=1771007594\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1029890/extras/3c64e4ffcd07f9fe296f1a80f52998c1.webm?t=1771007594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1029890/extras/3c64e4ffcd07f9fe296f1a80f52998c1.mp4?t=1771007594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事驱动探索 – 穿梭于世界各处，挖掘自身过往，揭开你被选中扮演这个角色的隐秘缘由。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >心理恐怖 – 眼前究竟是电影情节还是记忆欺骗？世界瞬息万变，唯有你能分辨真实与虚妄。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特远洋客轮场景 – 随着逐步深入船体深处，拍摄的电影场景将愈发超现实且令人毛骨悚然。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典而诡异的配乐 – 聆听由Arkadiusz Reikowski作曲、George Strezov指挥、Sofia Session Orchestra演奏的原创配乐。</p></li></ul>",
